Dialogue: 0,0:00:-01.00,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:37.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"North Block"\N"West Block" "South Block" "East Block"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings of those who are in anguish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are crushed by a dry cloud of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are those who seek hope,\Nand those who cling to hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their feelings cross each other,\Nuncertain what to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,marking an era of history ending in sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are those who would prevent war,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and those who would incite war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many different sensibilities\Nhave gathered at Alubarna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among them, at this very moment,\Nwere Usopp and Chopper,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whose battle against Mr. 4 and\NMiss Merry Christmas was unfolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Alabasta fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will it find true peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moment by moment, the goddess\Nof fate marks the final hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Big Opening Day Today!\NThe Copy-Copy Montage!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you lie to us, you haggy old mole!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he can be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he'd be beaten\Nby that sand-gator bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd think you'd need\Nsome grounds for saying
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that there's no way it could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the man who will be\Nking of the pirates someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why there's no way he\Ncan get his ticket punched here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-King of the pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"King-er-ates"? "K-rates"? "K"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't tell that foul story\Nin the Grand Line, ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm glad he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a stupid bastard,\Nwho didn't know his own place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A "ba"! He was a "ba"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for\Nyou to die, longnose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Molehill Highway!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...n-no m-m-matter how d-deathly\Nh-hideous his foe may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mole-Mole Impact!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...n-no matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...how slim a chance\Nhe has at beating them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look sharp! Take your batting stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your four-ton bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! Molehill...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Intersection #4!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weak are always weak,\Nno matter what they do! Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you want a go at it? That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll send you into the next world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like we did that\Ncowardly punk with the nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp is no coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:06:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times... when a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...must not run from a fight...\Nno matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like when... like when his\Nfriend's dream... is laughed at...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! Your head was\Nknocked in with a four-ton bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't still be alive!\NYou can't still be able to get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What trick did you use this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... isn't dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna be...\Nking of the pirates someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that's the one thing\NI won't let you laugh at!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! Looks like you still\Nhaven't learned your lesson yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time, Mr. 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm gonna let that happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you a transformation\Npoint that I've been saving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horn Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your determination,\Nat least, is praiseworthy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but no matter how resolute you might be,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't do anything in your shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Chopper...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get... b-behind... me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready, Mr. 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Special Attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes! Molehill...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Smoke Star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:08:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest... is up to you, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid took off his boots and got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Molehill Intersection #4!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Mr. 4! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack: Uso-Cho Hammer Comet!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone get a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:42.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alubarna - Southeast Gate Battle"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:50.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alubarna - Southeast Gate Battle"\N"Winners: Team Usopp & Chopper"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you okay?\N--Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koza! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've still got that\Nbullet from Nanohana...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a battlefield.\NSomething like that doesn't matter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to get one\Nof their horses somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get down this street,\Nand through the center of town,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be at the north block,\Nwhere the palace is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The palace? What are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demand that King Cobra surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! North block\Nis where the royal army's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,main force, including Chaka and Pell,\Nwill be! It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't even mustered\Nall of us together yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can wait until reinforcements get here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the other areas of town, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already too late as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Koza!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt! Are you with the rebel army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing ahead in\Nnorth block but the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not here as part of the battle,\Nleave this area of town at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening, woman?!\NThis is no playground!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is my father? Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...take me to where Chaka is!\NThere's something I want him to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deux!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Un... deux...! Un... deux...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a kick...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine, him being able to\Ncompete with my Ballet Kenpo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, if you want to get by,\Nyou'll have to defeat me, first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep pushing your luck like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Day in and day out, lesson, lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dancer's kenpo I've refined will\Nnot be beaten by the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use trying to escape from my fists!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ballet Kenpo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Degenerate Swan Dance Recital!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not getting anywhere like this.\NI'm gonna settle it right here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Collier Shoot!!\N--Un!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Épaule!!\N--Deux!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Côtelette!!\N--Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Selle!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Un!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Poitrine!!\N--Deux!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Gigot!!\N--Krah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ballet Kenpo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouton Shot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swan Arabesque!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:15:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Mouton Shot...\Nblocked by that bastard...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Swan Arabesque, stopped by\Nthat insignificant cook...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine! I mean business!\NFrom now on, I mean business!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what\Nmy ability is yet, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's amazing is the capacity\Nof my memory. If I use it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could make, say, this sort of montage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you see this, you will\Nlaugh until you collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the world's most unusual hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the world's most unusual eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's most unusual nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's most unusual mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, take a good, long look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand opening, today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:16:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Copy-Copy Montage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,90% of that was your own face, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've left yourself open!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop playing around, you dirty bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a heart?! You devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to mess\Naround with your craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Craft? That's nothing!\NCalling it a craft is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was someone like this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who, through friendship,\Nmade me powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Love is everything. People have\Nto have love. Your love needs me.\N--So that's it. I more or less get now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what you're going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, try to lay a hand on--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How could you?!\NThat was the face of your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you take your friends to be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, stupid? No matter\Nwho you change your form into,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're still you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the sort that's\Ncaught up by such images.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person is their soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person is their soul...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...refined!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed to have\Nbeen caught up by looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Even if I were to,\Nsay, set myself up as her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mellorine! Mellorine!\N--or any of your other friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mellorine! Mellorine!\N--it wouldn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mellorine! Mellorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's easy to read...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mellorine! Mello--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really easy to read...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--rine! Mellorine! Mel--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously easy to read...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true! The princess has come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, at a time such as this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you insane, Vivi-sama?! If we did that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we did that, what?\NThis land would be finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't, would it?\NThis place isn't Alabasta, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kingdom of Alabasta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the people who are\Nhurting each other now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of them that this\Nplace first became a country!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can stop this war,\Nthen that's good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! If we can draw everyone's\Neyes over here for a few seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then I will come up\Nwith something from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy... this palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying, Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This palace has a 4,000-year history!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't go through with\Nthis foolish idea, Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka-sama, don't let\Nyour judgment go astray!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king is not present!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot allow you\Nto do this on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, Your Majesty,\Nthe way things are headed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this country is in a mortal crisis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if it is? Are you\Nsaying we should wipe out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the people of this land,\Nwithout even knowing the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That indeed would be the\Ndestruction of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We set out for Rainbase, where Crocodile is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for saying so,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if we were to turn\Nagainst Crocodile now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be like pouring fuel\Non the flames of rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we would be attacking Rainbase,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the rebel army would come\Nagainst Alubarna Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so what if a rebel army\Nwere to take the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:21:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we, the royal army, were to fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we cut out the root of this,\Nthe country will surely rise again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not this castle that\Nwe should be protecting,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is the people of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the people are the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall do as you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to talk about it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:22:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even say half of it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm by your side, I glitter\Nevery time we share a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smile you gently gave me\Nwas a very happy and kind one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glory glory you're my shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're here, even\Nthese tears turn to courage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be strong,\NI want to share with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.10,0:22:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll make it there
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:22:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaah! Why are they coming after me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That dumb woman! Where did she go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.99,0:23:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This first-class cook of the sea\Nis nothing special, is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you my dancer's kenpo,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.33,0:23:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,developed during my daily lessons, lessons!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.33,0:23:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Transformed into Nami!\NBon Clay's Rapid-Fire Ballet Kenpo"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
